statements: SELECT * FROM quantum_experiment_progress;
SELECT experiment_name, experiment_date FROM quantum_experiment_progress;
SELECT experiment_id, experiment_name, experiment_date FROM quantum_experiment_progress WHERE success = TRUE;
SELECT experiment_name, communication_type FROM quantum_experiment_progress WHERE experiment_date >= '2023-01-01';
SELECT * FROM quantum_experiment_progress WHERE communication_type IS NULL;
SELECT experiment_id, experiment_name, experiment_date, success FROM quantum_experiment_progress WHERE success = TRUE
SELECT experiment_name, experiment_date FROM quantum_experiment_progress WHERE experiment_date >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY experiment_date DESC
SELECT * FROM quantum_experiment_progress WHERE experiment_name LIKE '%quantum%' AND communication_type IS NULL
SELECT COUNT(experiment_id) AS total_experiments, AVG(success) AS success_rate FROM quantum_experiment_progress WHERE success = TRUE
SELECT experiment_id, experiment_name, CASE WHEN success THEN 'Completed' ELSE 'Incomplete' END AS experiment_status FROM quantum_experiment_progress ORDER BY experiment_id DESC
SELECT * FROM experiment_data;
SELECT experiment_name, success FROM experiment_data WHERE success = TRUE;
SELECT experiment_id, experiment_name FROM experiment_data ORDER BY experiment_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM experiment_results WHERE result_code = 200 ORDER BY result_id ASC;
SELECT experiment_name, communication_method FROM experiment_data WHERE communication_method IS NOT NULL;
SELECT experiment_name, experiment_date, communication_method, success FROM experiment_data
SELECT * FROM experiment_results WHERE result_code > 100 ORDER BY experiment_id DESC
SELECT experiment_name, experiment_date, communication_method FROM experiment_data WHERE success = TRUE LIMIT 5
SELECT result_id, experiment_id, result_description FROM experiment_results WHERE result_code BETWEEN 200 AND 300
SELECT experiment_id, experiment_name, communication_method, success FROM experiment_data WHERE experiment_date >= '2022-01-01'
SELECT * FROM experiment_progress ORDER BY completion_date DESC, experiment_name;
SELECT experiment_id, progress_status FROM experiment_progress WHERE progress_status='Completed';
SELECT participant_name, age FROM participant_details WHERE gender='Male';
SELECT sender, receiver, message FROM communication_data WHERE timestamp > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT experiment_id, COUNT(participant_id) AS num_participants FROM participant_details GROUP BY experiment_id HAVING COUNT(participant_id) > 5;
SELECT * FROM experiment_progress ORDER BY completion_date DESC;
SELECT experiment_id, progress_status FROM experiment_progress WHERE progress_status = 'complete';
SELECT * FROM communication_data WHERE timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-01-31';
SELECT participant_name, age, gender FROM participant_details WHERE gender = 'female' ORDER BY age DESC;

SELECT experiment_name, progress_status FROM experiment_progress INNER JOIN participant_details ON experiment_progress.experiment_id = participant_details.experiment_id WHERE participant_name LIKE '%John%' AND progress_status = 'in progress';
SELECT * FROM experiments;
SELECT experiment_id, experiment_name FROM experiments WHERE experiment_status = 'completed';
SELECT experiment_date, experiment_name FROM experiments WHERE experiment_date >= '2021-01-01' ORDER BY experiment_date DESC;
SELECT lab_name, lab_location FROM labs ORDER BY lab_name ASC;
SELECT participant_name, participant_email FROM participants WHERE participant_email LIKE '%@example.com%';
SELECT experiment_name, experiment_date FROM experiments ORDER BY experiment_date DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM participants WHERE participant_email LIKE '%@example.com';
SELECT lab_name, lab_location FROM labs WHERE lab_location = 'New York';
SELECT e.experiment_name, m.measurement_type, m.measurement_result FROM experiments e JOIN measurements m ON e.experiment_id = m.experiment_id;
SELECT * FROM experiments JOIN measurements ON experiments.experiment_id = measurements.experiment_id ORDER BY experiment_date ASC, measurement_type DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM experiments;
SELECT experiment_name, experiment_date FROM experiments WHERE experiment_id = 1;
SELECT result_value, result_description FROM results WHERE result_id > 5;
SELECT participant_name, participant_age, participant_gender FROM participants WHERE participant_age BETWEEN 20 AND 30;
SELECT measurement_id, measurement_data FROM measurements ORDER BY measurement_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM experiments;
SELECT experiment_name, experiment_description FROM experiments WHERE experiment_date = '2022-09-15';
SELECT participant_name, participant_age, participant_gender FROM participants WHERE participant_age > 30 ORDER BY participant_name DESC;

SELECT m.measurement_date, r.result_value, r.result_description, p.participant_name FROM measurements m JOIN results r ON m.measurement_id = r.measurement_id JOIN participants p ON m.participant_id = p.participant_id WHERE p.participant_gender = 'Female';

SELECT e.experiment_name, p.participant_name, r.result_value FROM experiments e JOIN measurements m ON e.experiment_id = m.experiment_id JOIN results r ON m.measurement_id = r.measurement_id JOIN participants p ON m.participant_id = p.participant_id ORDER BY e.experiment_name ASC, r.result_value DESC;
